        <heading>3865.  Alternative writ</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 3865.  Alternative writ
Upon the filing of a petition for a writ of mandamus, the court shall order the issuance of an alternative writ directing the defendant to perform the act demanded or to show cause to the contrary.</p>
        </content>
